        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/25763237/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/25763237/" class="">第273页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/44878731/" class=" " title="肥兔叔叔">肥兔叔叔</a>
                (现在，请谈一谈你最爱的那个人。)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="25763237">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">缩头的，并非一定是乌龟，毒蛇在攻击之前，也要收脖子。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-04-14 10:58</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">4人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                缩头的，并非一定是乌龟，毒蛇在攻击之前，也要收脖子。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

